Output docs/assets/demo.gif

Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1200
Set Height 675
Set Padding 24
Set TypingSpeed 70ms
Set PlaybackSpeed 1.0

Type "ccx profile list"
Enter
Sleep 1.5s

Type "ccx use work"
Enter
Sleep 800ms

Type "claude --version"
Enter
Sleep 1.2s

Type "ccx usage"
Enter
Sleep 2s

Type "ccx dashboard"
Enter
Sleep 2.5s
